License: MIT License
Description: ##PyHTTP
        
        Very Minimal HTTP wrapper for Python.
        
        ##installation
        ```
        pip install pyrequest
        ```
        
        ##Usage
        
        ```python
          
        from pyhttp import Request
        
        r = Request("google.com").get()
        print r.status
        print r.content-type
        
        ```
        
